data.description: This dreamy starter home is ready for you to call it your own!  Located in popular Woodbury Woods, you'll love the feeling of being tucked away into a private suburb, while still being just minutes from all the conveniences and amenities you need! Owners have made many upgrades and improvements, including new LVP flooring throughout main, fresh interior paint, modern white baseboards, new doors and hardware, new DW and GD, and more.  Other details you'll appreciate include tray ceiling and bay window in LR, beautiful white washed brick fireplace with shiplap detail, wood accent wall in primary BR, spacious eat-in kitchen with pantry and pass through to DR, oversized laundry room, deck and fence new in 2020, and extended length garage. Easy access to I-80 makes commuting into Omaha a breeze.  Don't miss your chance to see this gem!
